<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="23" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph blockId="22.[189,1399,646,1392]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis box="[189,994,646,672]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Plantarum Imagines et Descriptiones Floram Russicam Illustrantes</emphasis>
1: 10, fig. 4 (
<bibRefCitation author="Trautvetter E. R. von" box="[1159,1362,646,672]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refId="ref39971" refString="Trautvetter E. R. von 1844. Plantarum Imagines et Descriptiones Floram Russicam Illustrantes. Vol. 1. E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgart. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 6362" type="book" year="1844">Trautvetter 1844</bibRefCitation>
). – 
<taxonomicName authority="Fisch. ex Ledeb., Denkschriften der Koniglich-Baierischen Botanischen Gesellschaft in Regensburg" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tetraphylla">
<emphasis box="[234,397,682,708]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. tetraphylla</emphasis>
Fisch. ex Ledeb., 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Denkschriften der Königlich-Baierischen Botanischen Gesellschaft in Regensburg</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
3 (2): 58 (
<bibRefCitation author="Ledebour C. F. von" box="[513,692,718,744]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="43 - 138" refId="ref37040" refString="Ledebour C. F. von 1841. Commentarius in J. G. Gmelini Floram. Denkschriften der Koniglich- Baierischen Botanischen Gesellschaft in Regensburg 3: 43 - 138." type="journal article" year="1841">Ledebour 1841</bibRefCitation>
) nom. nud. (sphalm. for 
<taxonomicName authority="Fisch." authorityName="Fisch." box="[971,1230,718,745]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[971,1149,718,744]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. heterophylla</emphasis>
Fisch.
</taxonomicName>
). – 
<taxonomicName authority="Ledeb., Flora Rossica" authorityName="Ledeb., Flora Rossica" authorityYear="1850" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="avellana" variety="davurica">
<emphasis box="[1266,1398,718,744]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. avellana</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[284,388,754,780]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">davurica</emphasis>
Ledeb., 
<emphasis box="[489,654,754,780]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Flora Rossica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
3 (2): 588 (
<bibRefCitation author="Ledebour C. F. von" box="[789,970,754,781]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="493 - 684" refId="ref37071" refString="Ledebour C. F. von 1850 [&quot; 1850 - 1851 &quot;]. Flora Rossica. Vol. 3 (2): 493 - 684. E. Schweizerbart, Stuttgart." type="journal article" year="1850">Ledebour 1850</bibRefCitation>
) [“ 
<date box="[1004,1148,753,780]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1850" valueMax="1851">1850–1851</date>
”]. – Original citation: “Delineavi ad specimina Argunensia sicca.” – Type: 
<collectingCountry box="[890,971,790,816]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, ad fl. Argun, s. coll., s.n. (lecto-, designated here: LE 
<date box="[470,596,826,852]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2787-01-01">01012787</date>
!). – Additional original material: 
<collectingCountry box="[979,1060,826,852]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, ad fl. Argun, [comm.? leg.?] 1836, 
<emphasis box="[310,504,861,888]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">F.E.L. Fischer 5</emphasis>
(BR!, P06810938!); 
<collectingCountry box="[761,842,862,888]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, ad alterum litteri Arguni in Dahuria chinensi, 1820, 
<emphasis box="[312,538,897,924]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C.F. von Ledebour</emphasis>
s.n. (P06810936!); 
<collectingCountry box="[786,867,897,923]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, Dahuria, ad fl. Argun, 
<emphasis box="[1163,1346,898,923]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">N. Turczaninov</emphasis>
s.n. (GOET!, P06810932!); 
<collectingCountry box="[524,605,933,959]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, in montosis ad fl. Argun, 1831, s. coll., s.n. (K!, LE 
<date box="[1266,1391,934,960]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2790-01-01">01012790</date>
!, MW0049851!); 
<collectingCountry box="[432,513,969,995]" name="Russia" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Russia</collectingCountry>
, in montosis Dahuriae ad fl. Argun, 1831, s. coll., s.n. (LE 
<date box="[1265,1391,969,996]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2785-01-01">01012785</date>
!, LE 
<date box="[273,399,1006,1032]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2788-01-01">01012788</date>
!); 
<collectingCountry box="[428,501,1005,1031]" name="China" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">China</collectingCountry>
, in Dahuriae Chinensi, ad fl. Argunum, 
<date box="[1008,1143,1006,1032]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1830" valueMax="1831">1830–1831</date>
, 
<emphasis box="[1161,1345,1006,1031]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">N. Turczaninov</emphasis>
s.n. (LE 
<date box="[281,407,1042,1068]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2784-01-01">01012784</date>
!, LE 
<date box="[461,587,1042,1068]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="2789-01-01">01012789</date>
!). – Note: the specimen designated as 
<typeStatus box="[1039,1147,1041,1067]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">lectotype</typeStatus>
is from Trautvetter’s herbarium, so it is certainly an original. It matches all characters given in the protologue as it is provided with leaves, nuts and young male catkins. The epithet 
<taxonomicName box="[987,1134,1113,1139]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[987,1134,1113,1139]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was validly published before in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C.Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" box="[344,437,1149,1175]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[344,437,1149,1175]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Corylus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a variety of 
<taxonomicName box="[612,746,1149,1176]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="avellana">
<emphasis box="[612,746,1149,1176]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. avellana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but it was used for a cultivar with deeply incised leaves (now ‘Urticifolia’). However, as neither Trautvetter nor Fischer dealt with a cultivar, but with a Siberian wild species, their name is not to be treated as a new combination (Art. 41.4, 
<bibRefCitation author="McNeill J. &amp; Barrie F. R. &amp; Buck W. R. &amp; Demoulin V. &amp; Greuter W. &amp; Hawksworth D. L. &amp; Herendeen P. S. &amp; Knapp S. &amp; Marhold K. &amp; Prado J. &amp; Prud'homme van Reine W. F. &amp; Smith G. F. &amp; Wiersema J. H. &amp; Turland N. J." pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refId="ref37892" refString="McNeill J., Barrie F. R., Buck W. R., Demoulin V., Greuter W., Hawksworth D. L., Herendeen P. S., Knapp S., Marhold K., Prado J., Prud'homme van Reine W. F., Smith G. F., Wiersema J. H. &amp; Turland N. J. 2012. International Code of Nomenclature for Algae, Fungi, and Plants (Melbourne Code). Koeltz Scientific Books, Koenigstein." type="book" year="2012">
McNeill 
<emphasis box="[1340,1399,1221,1247]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">et al.</emphasis>
2012
</bibRefCitation>
). Ledebour cited the protologue of 
<taxonomicName box="[723,907,1257,1283]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[723,907,1257,1283]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in total under his new name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ledeb., Flora Rossica" authorityYear="1850" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="avellana" variety="davurica">
<emphasis box="[1261,1398,1257,1283]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. avellana</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[286,390,1293,1319]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">davurica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. As he included the type of 
<taxonomicName box="[731,914,1293,1319]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[731,914,1293,1319]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, his name would be superfluous, but the combination to be adopted was not available due to 
<taxonomicName authority="Loudon (1838)" authorityName="Loudon, Arboretum et Fruticetum Britannicum" authorityYear="1838" box="[859,1395,1329,1356]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="avellana" variety="heterophylla">
<emphasis box="[859,996,1329,1355]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. avellana</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[1057,1204,1329,1355]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">heterophylla</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Loudon J. C." box="[1213,1395,1329,1355]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" refId="ref37669" refString="Loudon J. C. 1838. Arboretum et Fruticetum Britannicum. Vol. 3. Longman, Orme, Brown, Green, and Longmans, London. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 37723" type="book" year="1838">Loudon (1838)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Therefore, 
<taxonomicName authority="Ledeb." authorityName="Ledeb., Flora Rossica" authorityYear="1850" box="[365,750,1365,1392]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Corylus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="avellana" variety="davurica">
<emphasis box="[365,500,1365,1391]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C. avellana</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[558,662,1365,1391]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">davurica</emphasis>
Ledeb.
</taxonomicName>
is to be regarded as a nom. nov.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
